             was indicted for <rs id="t18170917-115-off564" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170917-115-off564" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170917-115-off564" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18170917-115-cd565" type="crimeDate">3d of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-115-off564 t18170917-115-cd565"></join>, one shawl, value 34s., and one piece of printed cotton, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170917-115-victim814" type="victimName">
                           Peter 
                           Goldborough
                        <interp inst="t18170917-115-victim814" type="surname" value="Goldborough"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18170917-115-victim814" type="given" value="Peter"></interp>
